3.summary: Convert ECG images into digital time-series data to improve cardiovascular care and access to health insights
3.title: Kaggle Competition: Convert ECG Images to Digital Time-Series Data
3.original_body:
Kaggle








Hi AswinVishwaaKB001,

For decades, electrocardiograms (ECGs) have been vital in diagnosing and  
treating heart disease. Yet, much of that data still exists only on paper  
as printouts, scans, or photographs, and remains inaccessible to modern AI  
systems. Today, you can help change that.

In this competition, your challenge is to build models that convert ECG  
images into digital time-series data. By doing so, you'll help bridge the  
gap between analog medical records and data-driven healthcare innovation.





Total Prizes:

$50,000


Entry Deadline:

January 15, 2026




Learn More



Your work could help unlock billions of historical ECG images, support  
improved cardiovascular care and expand access to critical health insights,  
particularly in areas where digital records are limited.

Good luck,

Sohier Dane
Kaggle Data Scientist



Kaggle, Inc 1600 Amphitheatre Pkwy Mountain View, CA 94043

This email was sent to aswinvishwaa415@gmail.com because you indicated that  
you'd like to receive news and updates about Kaggle. If you don't want to  
receive these emails in the future, please unsubscribe here. You can also  
change your preferences on your account's profile page by logging in at  
kaggle.com.

1.summary: A 5-day hands-on course on building and deploying AI agents, no-cost, designed by Google researchers and engineers.
1.title: 5-Day AI Agents Intensive Course with Google
1.original_body:
Kaggle








Hi AswinVishwaaKB001,

Ready to learn how to build and deploy your own AI agents?

Join the 5-Day AI Agents Intensive Course with Google, happening from  
November 10 to 14. This no-cost, hands-on program is designed by Google  
researchers and engineers for a deep dive into AI agents.


Register Here






Here's what you'll get:


📚 Daily Assignments: White papers, podcasts, codelabs that you can  
complete at your own pace
💬 Discord Discussions: Connect with peers and Google experts
🎥 Daily Livestream Seminars and AMAs: Q&A with course creators on Kaggle's  
YouTube


More info on the event website here.

Hope to see you there!

The Kaggle Team
